<div class="privacy-policy">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 2025</p>

    <section>
        <h3>Overview</h3>
        <p>
            This Privacy Policy describes how PDF Text Extraction Comparison ("we", "us", or "our")
            handles information when you use our service. We are committed to protecting your privacy
            and being transparent about our practices.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3>File Uploads</h3>
        <p>
            <strong>We do not store your uploaded files.</strong> When you upload a PDF for text extraction comparison:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Files are processed entirely in memory</li>
            <li>Files are immediately discarded after processing completes</li>
            <li>No copies of your files are saved to disk or any storage system</li>
            <li>No file contents are transmitted to third parties</li>
            <li>Processing occurs on our servers and results are returned directly to your browser</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Once you close your browser session or navigate away from the page, all data related to your
            uploaded files is permanently gone.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We may automatically collect limited technical information when you visit our site:</p>
